race.comment: MIN SHAN (1) Was strong to the line when winning last time here. Keeping a perfect win record the last 2 runs. Camilio Ospina and Ahmed Mohamoud command respect as a pairing. Key player. KAWAFILL (10) Won by a big margin last time at Taif and going back up in distance. Has hit top form this preparation with 2 wins from 2 runs. Good prospects. ARKAAN ALDER'EYAH (9) Was strong to the line when winning last start at this venue. Jockey Alexis Moreno consistently rides well for this stable. Must be considered. MUTAFEF (4) Looked good when 3rd last run at this track. Racing consistently this preparation. Jockey Ricardo Ferreira is a strong choice aboard. Worth a ticket.
